 Burnpur 258. Aryan 262/4 (Satyen Bhattacharya 

 97). Aryan won by 6 wkts.

 The 15th Mercantile Mixed Basketball Tournament will get underway at the Rangers ground on Saturday. Five teams ? Airtel, ABN Amro Bank, ITC, IBM Club and TCS ? will play a round-robin league, followed by the semis featuring the top four. The final will come off on March 4.

 West Bengal Police overcame Xaverians 70-46 in a state basketball league match at the WBBA courts on Thursday.

